R

Rattata - class Rattata.
A Rattata is a Pokemon that maintains information about its level, speed, strength, special, defense, total health, current health, experience points, name, attack names, and it's pokemon number.
Rattata(int) - Constructor for class Rattata
Creates a Rattata with all attributes based on the Rattata's level specified by x.
